The paper discusses a new method for semi-supervised learning using Self-Organizing Maps (SOM) for clustering and classification. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The method also involves adjusting to local variance, which could be related to neural networks (cs.NE) and computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper mentions using the method for text classification, which could fall under computational linguistics (cs.CL).
